        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&quot;data&quot;:&quot;@startuml\n&#39; --- High Visibility Textbook Style ---\nskinparam linetype ortho\nskinparam shadowing false\nskinparam DefaultFontName \&quot;Courier New\&quot;\nskinparam DefaultFontSize 14\nskinparam rectangle {\n    BackgroundColor white\n    BorderColor black\n    BorderThickness 1.5\n}\n\n&#39; --- Tables ---\n\nrectangle \&quot;**USER**\\n| &lt;u&gt;userId&lt;/u&gt; | username | password | email | phone | role | auth | isFrozen |\&quot; as User\n\nrectangle \&quot;**USER_PERMISSIONS**\\n| &lt;u&gt;userId&lt;/u&gt; (FK) | &lt;u&gt;permission&lt;/u&gt; |\&quot; as Perm\n\nrectangle \&quot;**DOCTOR**\\n| &lt;u&gt;userId&lt;/u&gt; (FK) | specialization | rating | bio |\&quot; as Doctor\n\nrectangle \&quot;**DOCTOR_CERTIFICATES**\\n| &lt;u&gt;userId&lt;/u&gt; (FK) | &lt;u&gt;certificate_url&lt;/u&gt; |\&quot; as Cert\n\nrectangle \&quot;**PATIENT**\\n| &lt;u&gt;userId&lt;/u&gt; (FK) | history_id (FK) |\&quot; as Patient\n\nrectangle \&quot;**HISTORY_D**\\n| &lt;u&gt;id&lt;/u&gt; | history_text | note |\&quot; as History\n\nrectangle \&quot;**AVAILABILITY_SLOT**\\n| &lt;u&gt;id&lt;/u&gt; | doctor_id (FK) | start_time | end_time | duration_mins |\&quot; as Slot\n\nrectangle \&quot;**SLOT_DAYS**\\n| &lt;u&gt;slot_id&lt;/u&gt; (FK) | &lt;u&gt;day_name&lt;/u&gt; |\&quot; as SlotDay\n\nrectangle \&quot;**APPOINTMENT**\\n| &lt;u&gt;id&lt;/u&gt; | slot_id (FK) | patient_id (FK) | doctor_id (FK) | note | date | time_slot |\&quot; as Appt\n\nrectangle \&quot;**APPOINTED_PATIENT**\\n| &lt;u&gt;id&lt;/u&gt; | doctor_id (FK) | patient_id (FK) | patient_name |\&quot; as Appointed\n\n&#39; --- PK -&gt; FK Connections ---\n\nUser --&gt; Perm\nUser --&gt; Doctor\nUser --&gt; Patient\n\nDoctor --&gt; Cert\nDoctor --&gt; Slot\nSlot --&gt; SlotDay\n\nHistory --&gt; Patient\n\nDoctor --&gt; Appt\nPatient --&gt; Appt\nSlot --&gt; Appt\n\nDoctor --&gt; Appointed\nPatient --&gt; Appointed\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&quot;format&q